channel.title: [508/525]Dark-PKz Development[508/525]
channel.description:
Hey guys and im looking for a great bunch of people to help out and be a part of a development team. I used to code 317's alot and got bored becuase they are soooo easy to code so now, i want a challenge. For this development team we will need:
[ul]A Coder - To help out on the server and client(cause im a newbie "517" Coder) A Website Developer A Client Maker A Website GFX Creator And hopefully a 24/7 hoster[/ul]
In your application you must include: 1. The Experience 2. What role you would like to fill 3 Examples of your work 4. Age 5. Name 6. Times on (GMT)
Thanks for Reading! Also if your interested and want to know more or ask me a few questions add me on either: dark-pkz@hotmail.co.uk or chrisncal_@hotmail.co.uk
